Tronmiota ( TronBot x Miotabot )

"tronbot" TRON This robot is a robot that has air weapons equipment. has wings that are used as shields from enemy attacks. and has many deadly mine tails, and is equipped with razor blades and gear, to immobilize the enemy.

"miotabot" a change from bees, robots can be used to detect land mines. Because, this robot can smell trinitrotoluene or TNT from a distance of 100 kilometers. These two facts show that this robot is very careful and very sensitive to potential dangers.
